title: Episode 361: Bad N Ghetto (Feat. Cardi B)
itunes:title: Episode 361: Bad N Ghetto (Feat. Cardi B)
description:
Cardi B joins the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote her new single 'Hot Shit" featuring Kanye West and Lil Durk. Cardi opens up about falling in love with Offset, getting robbed by a broke ex, being unable to admit when she's wrong, and much more. Enjoy!
